(deflayer symbols
     _    @'   @<   @>    @''  @|   @&   @`   [    ]    @%
     _    @!   -    @+    @=   @?   @#   @:   S-9 S-0   S-2   _
     _    @^   /    @*    \    @bk  @~   @$   @{   @}   .     _
     _    _    _              _              _    _    _
)
